sub_title: Professional with experience in Finance Control, Procurement, and Supply Chain.
summary:
Professional with the passion and energy to exceed expectations. With experience in Supply Chain Finance, Business Partnering and procurement. Work and academic international experience in Venezuela, USA, and Europe.

Fluent in Spanish and English, Work permit in the EU (Italian and Venezuelan Nationality).
